{
  "stem": "512.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have given certain things to the neighbors if they wanted to hide it for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother had a lot of-- she came from a wealthy family, as a I told you-- a lot of hand embroidered things, which that was part of the trousseau for her at that time that everything was embroidered.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Her linens, her tablecloths, her towels, everything was hand made.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she gave them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They should hide it for it, that maybe she will-- somebody will return.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We never, definitely never, never thought-- but my father-- but he didn't talk about it-- saw what happened.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he feared tremendously that this is going to happen to our part of the country also.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they begged the minister from the church-- because there was illness-- that he should declare that it is a-- because a couple of people had typhus, that he should declare the community as a with a contagious disease.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They should be held back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He refused.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was extremely anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sundays were the most horrible, horrible days because he would preach in the church, and then they would go out on the church and find their victims.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Jews were hidden, locked up in their homes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were-- they were terrified, because that's when he antagonized them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stayed a great deal with my grandmother because she was a bit old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was alone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, my grandmother still had-- she had a big farm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one time she had a lot of help.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in the later years, she had nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I had to help out with those chores.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my grandmother passed away in 1943.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a very grateful thing that she didn't have to go through.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had-- also we had some cattle.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
